It can cure strange illnesses of energy.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:28.360
Only knotweed is hard to find in Songling Town.

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:31.680
But I recall a small stream on the southern slope.

00:02:32.040 --> 00:02:33.840
At this time of year,

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:35.080
it should be possible to harvest some.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.840
I've never been to the southern slope.

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:39.080
